       </section>
       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function ($) {
         'use strict';
 
         var hiddenIds = {};
 
         var getCookie = function (cname) {
             var name = cname + '=';
             var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
             for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
                 var c = ca[i];
                 while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
                     c = c.substring(1);
                 }
                 if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
                     return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
                 }
             }
             return '';
         };
 
         var setCookie = function (cname, cvalue, exdays) {
             var d = new Date();
             d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = 'expires=' + d.toUTCString();
             document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + '; ' + expires + ';path=/';
         };
 
         var addForumCloseLinks = function () {
             $('.cForumRow .ipsDataList .ipsDataItem').each(function () {
                 var catId = $(this).parent().closest('.cForumRow').data('categoryid');
                 var forumId = $(this).data('forumid');
                 $(this).append('<button onclick="hideForum(' + catId + ', ' + forumId + ')" class="forum-hide-link">X</button>');
             });
         };
 
         var saveHiddenIds = function () {
             var value = '';
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (cat_id, values) {
                 for (var j = 0; j < values.length; ++j) {
                     value += cat_id + '_' + values[j] + ';';
                 }
             });
 
             setCookie('hiddenIds', encodeURIComponent(value), 360);
         };
 
         window.hideForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
             }
             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         window.showForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] != null) {
                 var temp = hiddenIds[catId];
                 for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; ++i) {
                     if (forumId == temp[i]) {
                         hiddenIds[catId].splice(i, 1);
                         break;
                     }
                 }
             }
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         var renderHiddenForums = function () {
             $('.hidden-forum-container').hide();
 
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (catId, forumIds) {
                 var holder = $('[data-categoryid="' + catId + '"]');
                 holder.removeClass('has-hidden-forums');
                 if (holder.length > 0) {
                     holder.find('.ipsDataItem').show();
                     holder.addClass('has-hidden-forums');
 
                     var container = holder.find('.hidden-forum-container');
                     if (container.length == 0) {
                         container = $('<div class="hidden-forum-container"></div>')
                         container.insertAfter(holder.find('>ol'));
                     }
                     container.html('');
 
                     if(forumIds.length > 0) {
                         container.show();
                     }
                     $.each(forumIds, function (key, value) {
                         var row = $('[data-forumid="' + value + '"]');
                         row.hide();
                         var title = row.find('.ipsDataItem_title a').text();
                         container.append('<button onclick="showForum(' + catId + ', ' + value + ')" class="forum-show-link">' + title + '</button>');
                     });
                     holder.find('.ipsDataList > li:visible').removeClass('even').filter(function(index, element){
                         return index % 2;
                     }).addClass('even')
                 }
             });
         };
 
 
         var checkForumCookies = function () {
             var cookie = getCookie('hiddenIds');
             cookie = decodeURIComponent(cookie);
             if (cookie != null) {
                 var temp = cookie.split(';');
                 if ((temp != null) && (temp.length > 0)) {
                     for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; i++) {
                         var values = temp[i].split('_');
                         var catId = String(values[0]);
                         var forumId = String(values[1]);
                         if (catId != '') {
                             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
                             }
                             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
                         }
                     }
                 }
             }
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         $(document).ready(function () {
             addForumCloseLinks();
             checkForumCookies();
         });
 
     }(jQuery));
       </script>

          <h2 class="ipsType_sectionTitle ipsType_reset cForumTitle">

          <h2 class="ipsType_sectionTitle ipsType_reset cForumTitle">

          <ol class="ipsDataList ipsDataList_large ipsDataList_zebra ipsAreaBackground_reset" data-role="forums">
           <li class="cForumRow ipsDataItem ipsDataItem_responsivePhoto ipsClearfix" data-forumid="204">
            <div class="ipsDataItem_icon ipsDataItem_category">
             <img class="ipsItemStatus ipsItemStatus_custom ipsItemStatus_read" src="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/uploads/monthly_2016_08/205-vor_der_euro_2016.png.acc88358cc47f866dedebab1017a65e9.png"/>

             <h4 class="ipsDataItem_title ipsType_large ipsType_break">
              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/204-europameisterschaft-2016-in-frankreich/">

           <li class="cForumRow ipsDataItem ipsDataItem_responsivePhoto ipsClearfix" data-forumid="122">
            <div class="ipsDataItem_icon ipsDataItem_category">
             <span class="ipsItemStatus ipsItemStatus_large cForumIcon_normal ipsItemStatus_read">

            <div class="ipsDataItem_main">
             <h4 class="ipsDataItem_title ipsType_large ipsType_break">
              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/122-ehemalige-foren/">
               Ehemalige Foren

              <a class="ipsUserPhoto ipsUserPhoto_tiny" data-ipshover="" data-ipshover-target="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/?do=hovercard" href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/" title="Gehe zu blauweiss78s Profil">

               Der SV Pasching 16 in der …

              Von
              <a class="ipsType_break" data-ipshover="" data-ipshover-target="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/?do=hovercard&amp;referrer=https%253A%252F%252Fwww.austriansoccerboard.at%252F" href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/" title="Gehe zu blauweiss78s Profil">

           <!-- block: "ad_index_after_forum_id_68" -->

           <!-- block: "ad_index_after_forum_position_10" -->
          </div>

       </section>
       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function ($) {
         'use strict';
 
         var hiddenIds = {};
 
         var getCookie = function (cname) {
             var name = cname + '=';
             var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
             for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
                 var c = ca[i];
                 while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
                     c = c.substring(1);
                 }
                 if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
                     return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
                 }
             }
             return '';
         };
 
         var setCookie = function (cname, cvalue, exdays) {
             var d = new Date();
             d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = 'expires=' + d.toUTCString();
             document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + '; ' + expires + ';path=/';
         };
 
         var addForumCloseLinks = function () {
             $('.cForumRow .ipsDataList .ipsDataItem').each(function () {
                 var catId = $(this).parent().closest('.cForumRow').data('categoryid');
                 var forumId = $(this).data('forumid');
                 $(this).append('<button onclick="hideForum(' + catId + ', ' + forumId + ')" class="forum-hide-link">X</button>');
             });
         };
 
         var saveHiddenIds = function () {
             var value = '';
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (cat_id, values) {
                 for (var j = 0; j < values.length; ++j) {
                     value += cat_id + '_' + values[j] + ';';
                 }
             });
 
             setCookie('hiddenIds', encodeURIComponent(value), 360);
         };
 
         window.hideForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
             }
             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         window.showForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] != null) {
                 var temp = hiddenIds[catId];
                 for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; ++i) {
                     if (forumId == temp[i]) {
                         hiddenIds[catId].splice(i, 1);
                         break;
                     }
                 }
             }
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         var renderHiddenForums = function () {
             $('.hidden-forum-container').hide();
 
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (catId, forumIds) {
                 var holder = $('[data-categoryid="' + catId + '"]');
                 holder.removeClass('has-hidden-forums');
                 if (holder.length > 0) {
                     holder.find('.ipsDataItem').show();
                     holder.addClass('has-hidden-forums');
 
                     var container = holder.find('.hidden-forum-container');
                     if (container.length == 0) {
                         container = $('<div class="hidden-forum-container"></div>')
                         container.insertAfter(holder.find('>ol'));
                     }
                     container.html('');
 
                     if(forumIds.length > 0) {
                         container.show();
                     }
                     $.each(forumIds, function (key, value) {
                         var row = $('[data-forumid="' + value + '"]');
                         row.hide();
                         var title = row.find('.ipsDataItem_title a').text();
                         container.append('<button onclick="showForum(' + catId + ', ' + value + ')" class="forum-show-link">' + title + '</button>');
                     });
                     holder.find('.ipsDataList > li:visible').removeClass('even').filter(function(index, element){
                         return index % 2;
                     }).addClass('even')
                 }
             });
         };
 
 
         var checkForumCookies = function () {
             var cookie = getCookie('hiddenIds');
             cookie = decodeURIComponent(cookie);
             if (cookie != null) {
                 var temp = cookie.split(';');
                 if ((temp != null) && (temp.length > 0)) {
                     for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; i++) {
                         var values = temp[i].split('_');
                         var catId = String(values[0]);
                         var forumId = String(values[1]);
                         if (catId != '') {
                             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
                             }
                             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
                         }
                     }
                 }
             }
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         $(document).ready(function () {
             addForumCloseLinks();
             checkForumCookies();
         });
 
     }(jQuery));
       </script>

          <h2 class="ipsType_sectionTitle ipsType_reset cForumTitle">

          <h2 class="ipsType_sectionTitle ipsType_reset cForumTitle">
           <a class="ipsPos_right ipsJS_show ipsType_noUnderline cForumToggle" data-action="toggleCategory" data-ipstooltip="" href="#" title="Diese Kategorie ein-/ausklappen">
           </a>
           <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/70-fans/">
            Fans
           </a>
          </h2>
          <ol class="ipsDataList ipsDataList_large ipsDataList_zebra ipsAreaBackground_reset" data-role="forums">
           <li class="cForumRow ipsDataItem ipsDataItem_responsivePhoto ipsClearfix" data-forumid="57">
            <div class="ipsDataItem_icon ipsDataItem_category">
             <img class="ipsItemStatus ipsItemStatus_custom ipsItemStatus_read" src="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/uploads/monthly_2016_08/57-fotos_videos_fan_tv.png.20b0b7a22e23950acd68207b68c753ac.png"/>
            </div>
            <div class="ipsDataItem_main">
             <h4 class="ipsDataItem_title ipsType_large ipsType_break">
              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/57-fotos-videos-und-fan-tv/">
               Fotos, Videos und Fan-TV
              </a>
             </h4>
             <div class="ipsDataItem_meta ipsType_richText ipsContained">
              <p>
               In diesem Channel könnt ihr selbstgeschossene Fotos und selbstgedrehte Videos posten. Auch Choreo-Wahlen und Fan-TV sind in diesem Forum zu finden.
               <br/>
               Bitte lest vor dem Posten in diesem Forum die Forums-Richtlinien.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ipsDataItem_stats ipsDataItem_statsLarge">
             <dl>

               21.204

             <li>
              <a class="ipsUserPhoto ipsUserPhoto_tiny" data-ipshover="" data-ipshover-target="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/8099-brucki/?do=hovercard" href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/8099-brucki/" title="Gehe zu Bruckis Profil">

             <h4 class="ipsDataItem_title ipsType_large ipsType_break">
              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/122-ehemalige-foren/">
               Ehemalige Foren
              </a>
             </h4>

               Hier findet ihr ehemalige Foren des ASB, die seit 2007 temporär oder fix archiviert wurden.

          <div class="ad-box ad-index-after-forum">
           <!-- block: "ad_index_after_forum_position_10" -->
          </div>
         </li>
        </ol>
       </section>
       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function ($) {
         'use strict';
 
         var hiddenIds = {};
 
         var getCookie = function (cname) {
             var name = cname + '=';
             var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
             for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
                 var c = ca[i];
                 while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
                     c = c.substring(1);
                 }
                 if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
                     return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
                 }
             }
             return '';
         };
 
         var setCookie = function (cname, cvalue, exdays) {
             var d = new Date();
             d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = 'expires=' + d.toUTCString();
             document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + '; ' + expires + ';path=/';
         };
 
         var addForumCloseLinks = function () {
             $('.cForumRow .ipsDataList .ipsDataItem').each(function () {
                 var catId = $(this).parent().closest('.cForumRow').data('categoryid');
                 var forumId = $(this).data('forumid');
                 $(this).append('<button onclick="hideForum(' + catId + ', ' + forumId + ')" class="forum-hide-link">X</button>');
             });
         };
 
         var saveHiddenIds = function () {
             var value = '';
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (cat_id, values) {
                 for (var j = 0; j < values.length; ++j) {
                     value += cat_id + '_' + values[j] + ';';
                 }
             });
 
             setCookie('hiddenIds', encodeURIComponent(value), 360);
         };
 
         window.hideForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
             }
             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         window.showForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] != null) {
                 var temp = hiddenIds[catId];
                 for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; ++i) {
                     if (forumId == temp[i]) {
                         hiddenIds[catId].splice(i, 1);
                         break;
                     }
                 }
             }
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         var renderHiddenForums = function () {
             $('.hidden-forum-container').hide();
 
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (catId, forumIds) {
                 var holder = $('[data-categoryid="' + catId + '"]');
                 holder.removeClass('has-hidden-forums');
                 if (holder.length > 0) {
                     holder.find('.ipsDataItem').show();
                     holder.addClass('has-hidden-forums');
 
                     var container = holder.find('.hidden-forum-container');
                     if (container.length == 0) {
                         container = $('<div class="hidden-forum-container"></div>')
                         container.insertAfter(holder.find('>ol'));
                     }
                     container.html('');
 
                     if(forumIds.length > 0) {
                         container.show();
                     }
                     $.each(forumIds, function (key, value) {
                         var row = $('[data-forumid="' + value + '"]');
                         row.hide();
                         var title = row.find('.ipsDataItem_title a').text();
                         container.append('<button onclick="showForum(' + catId + ', ' + value + ')" class="forum-show-link">' + title + '</button>');
                     });
                     holder.find('.ipsDataList > li:visible').removeClass('even').filter(function(index, element){
                         return index % 2;
                     }).addClass('even')
                 }
             });
         };
 
 
         var checkForumCookies = function () {
             var cookie = getCookie('hiddenIds');
             cookie = decodeURIComponent(cookie);
             if (cookie != null) {
                 var temp = cookie.split(';');
                 if ((temp != null) && (temp.length > 0)) {
                     for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; i++) {
                         var values = temp[i].split('_');
                         var catId = String(values[0]);
                         var forumId = String(values[1]);
                         if (catId != '') {
                             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
                             }
                             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
                         }
                     }
                 }
             }
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         $(document).ready(function () {
             addForumCloseLinks();
             checkForumCookies();
         });
 
     }(jQuery));
       </script>

          <div class="kurier-container">
           <div class="kurier-header">
            <a href="https://kurier.at/sport/fussball" target="_blank">
             <img src="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/uploads/pages_media/1_kurier-logo.png"/>

          <link href="//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=PT+Sans+Narrow:400,700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>
          <script type="text/javascript">
           (function($) {
       $.ajax({
         url: '/rss2json.php',
         dataType: 'json',
         success: function (data) {
           if (data.items) {
             var container = $('#kurier-rss-list');
             $.each(data.items, function (i, e) {
               if (i>2){return false;}
               var category = e.categories.pop();
               var li = $('<li />');
               var link = $('<a />', { href: e.link, target: '_blank' });
               link.append('<span class="kurier-link-text">' + e.title + '</span>');
               li.append(link);
               container.append(li);
             });
           }
         }
       });
       
       /* Google AJAX Feed API 
       $.ajax({

           <li class="cForumRow ipsDataItem ipsDataItem_responsivePhoto ipsClearfix" data-forumid="122">
            <div class="ipsDataItem_icon ipsDataItem_category">

            <div class="ipsDataItem_main">
             <h4 class="ipsDataItem_title ipsType_large ipsType_break">
              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/122-ehemalige-foren/">

       </section>
       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function ($) {
         'use strict';
 
         var hiddenIds = {};
 
         var getCookie = function (cname) {
             var name = cname + '=';
             var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
             for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
                 var c = ca[i];
                 while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
                     c = c.substring(1);
                 }
                 if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
                     return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
                 }
             }
             return '';
         };
 
         var setCookie = function (cname, cvalue, exdays) {
             var d = new Date();
             d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = 'expires=' + d.toUTCString();
             document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + '; ' + expires + ';path=/';
         };
 
         var addForumCloseLinks = function () {
             $('.cForumRow .ipsDataList .ipsDataItem').each(function () {
                 var catId = $(this).parent().closest('.cForumRow').data('categoryid');
                 var forumId = $(this).data('forumid');
                 $(this).append('<button onclick="hideForum(' + catId + ', ' + forumId + ')" class="forum-hide-link">X</button>');
             });
         };
 
         var saveHiddenIds = function () {
             var value = '';
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (cat_id, values) {
                 for (var j = 0; j < values.length; ++j) {
                     value += cat_id + '_' + values[j] + ';';
                 }
             });
 
             setCookie('hiddenIds', encodeURIComponent(value), 360);
         };
 
         window.hideForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
             }
             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         window.showForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] != null) {
                 var temp = hiddenIds[catId];
                 for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; ++i) {
                     if (forumId == temp[i]) {
                         hiddenIds[catId].splice(i, 1);
                         break;
                     }
                 }
             }
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         var renderHiddenForums = function () {
             $('.hidden-forum-container').hide();
 
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (catId, forumIds) {
                 var holder = $('[data-categoryid="' + catId + '"]');
                 holder.removeClass('has-hidden-forums');
                 if (holder.length > 0) {
                     holder.find('.ipsDataItem').show();
                     holder.addClass('has-hidden-forums');
 
                     var container = holder.find('.hidden-forum-container');
                     if (container.length == 0) {
                         container = $('<div class="hidden-forum-container"></div>')
                         container.insertAfter(holder.find('>ol'));
                     }
                     container.html('');
 
                     if(forumIds.length > 0) {
                         container.show();
                     }
                     $.each(forumIds, function (key, value) {
                         var row = $('[data-forumid="' + value + '"]');
                         row.hide();
                         var title = row.find('.ipsDataItem_title a').text();
                         container.append('<button onclick="showForum(' + catId + ', ' + value + ')" class="forum-show-link">' + title + '</button>');
                     });
                     holder.find('.ipsDataList > li:visible').removeClass('even').filter(function(index, element){
                         return index % 2;
                     }).addClass('even')
                 }
             });
         };
 
 
         var checkForumCookies = function () {
             var cookie = getCookie('hiddenIds');
             cookie = decodeURIComponent(cookie);
             if (cookie != null) {
                 var temp = cookie.split(';');
                 if ((temp != null) && (temp.length > 0)) {
                     for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; i++) {
                         var values = temp[i].split('_');
                         var catId = String(values[0]);
                         var forumId = String(values[1]);
                         if (catId != '') {
                             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
                             }
                             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
                         }
                     }
                 }
             }
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         $(document).ready(function () {
             addForumCloseLinks();
             checkForumCookies();
         });
 
     }(jQuery));
       </script>

              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/32-beisl/">
               Beisl
              </a>

             <div class="ipsDataItem_meta ipsType_richText ipsContained">
              <p>
               Hier könnt Ihr Euch mal so richtig die Meinung sagen. Dieses Forum ist wesentlich uneingeschränkter als die anderen Foren, dennoch gibt es Grenzen.
               <br/>
               Über Politik darf NUR hier diskutiert werden !
               <br/>
               <b>
                Nur für registrierte Mitglieder sichtbar!
               </b>
              </p>

           <li class="cForumRow ipsDataItem ipsDataItem_responsivePhoto ipsClearfix" data-forumid="122">
            <div class="ipsDataItem_icon ipsDataItem_category">

            <div class="ipsDataItem_main">
             <h4 class="ipsDataItem_title ipsType_large ipsType_break">
              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/forum/122-ehemalige-foren/">
               Ehemalige Foren

            <ul class="ipsDataItem_lastPoster ipsDataItem_withPhoto">
             <li>
              <a class="ipsUserPhoto ipsUserPhoto_tiny" data-ipshover="" data-ipshover-target="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/?do=hovercard" href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/" title="Gehe zu blauweiss78s Profil">
               <img alt="blauweiss78" itemprop="image" src="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/uploads/set_resources_3/84c1e40ea0e759e3f1505eb1788ddf3c_default_photo.png"/>
              </a>
             </li>
             <li>
              <a href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/topic/111378-der-sv-pasching-16-in-der-2-klasse/?do=getNewComment" title="Der SV Pasching 16 in der 2. Klasse">
               Der SV Pasching 16 in der …
              </a>
             </li>
             <li class="ipsType_blendLinks">
              Von
              <a class="ipsType_break" data-ipshover="" data-ipshover-target="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/?do=hovercard&amp;referrer=https%253A%252F%252Fwww.austriansoccerboard.at%252F" href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/profile/37767-blauweiss78/" title="Gehe zu blauweiss78s Profil">
               blauweiss78
              </a>

             <li class="ipsType_light">
              <a class="ipsType_blendLinks" href="https://www.austriansoccerboard.at/topic/111378-der-sv-pasching-16-in-der-2-klasse/?do=getLastComment" title="Gehe zum letzten Beitrag">
               <time data-short="3 Ta" datetime="2018-06-20T12:29:56Z" title="20.06.2018 12:29 ">
                Mittwoch um 12:29
               </time>

          <div class="ad-box ad-index-after-forum">
           <!-- block: "ad_index_after_forum_id_68" -->
          </div>
          <div class="ad-box ad-index-after-forum">
           <!-- block: "ad_index_after_forum_position_10" -->
          </div>
         </li>
        </ol>
       </section>
       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function ($) {
         'use strict';
 
         var hiddenIds = {};
 
         var getCookie = function (cname) {
             var name = cname + '=';
             var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
             for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
                 var c = ca[i];
                 while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
                     c = c.substring(1);
                 }
                 if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
                     return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
                 }
             }
             return '';
         };
 
         var setCookie = function (cname, cvalue, exdays) {
             var d = new Date();
             d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = 'expires=' + d.toUTCString();
             document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + '; ' + expires + ';path=/';
         };
 
         var addForumCloseLinks = function () {
             $('.cForumRow .ipsDataList .ipsDataItem').each(function () {
                 var catId = $(this).parent().closest('.cForumRow').data('categoryid');
                 var forumId = $(this).data('forumid');
                 $(this).append('<button onclick="hideForum(' + catId + ', ' + forumId + ')" class="forum-hide-link">X</button>');
             });
         };
 
         var saveHiddenIds = function () {
             var value = '';
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (cat_id, values) {
                 for (var j = 0; j < values.length; ++j) {
                     value += cat_id + '_' + values[j] + ';';
                 }
             });
 
             setCookie('hiddenIds', encodeURIComponent(value), 360);
         };
 
         window.hideForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
             }
             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         window.showForum = function (catId, forumId) {
             if (hiddenIds[catId] != null) {
                 var temp = hiddenIds[catId];
                 for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; ++i) {
                     if (forumId == temp[i]) {
                         hiddenIds[catId].splice(i, 1);
                         break;
                     }
                 }
             }
             saveHiddenIds();
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         var renderHiddenForums = function () {
             $('.hidden-forum-container').hide();
 
             $.each(hiddenIds, function (catId, forumIds) {
                 var holder = $('[data-categoryid="' + catId + '"]');
                 holder.removeClass('has-hidden-forums');
                 if (holder.length > 0) {
                     holder.find('.ipsDataItem').show();
                     holder.addClass('has-hidden-forums');
 
                     var container = holder.find('.hidden-forum-container');
                     if (container.length == 0) {
                         container = $('<div class="hidden-forum-container"></div>')
                         container.insertAfter(holder.find('>ol'));
                     }
                     container.html('');
 
                     if(forumIds.length > 0) {
                         container.show();
                     }
                     $.each(forumIds, function (key, value) {
                         var row = $('[data-forumid="' + value + '"]');
                         row.hide();
                         var title = row.find('.ipsDataItem_title a').text();
                         container.append('<button onclick="showForum(' + catId + ', ' + value + ')" class="forum-show-link">' + title + '</button>');
                     });
                     holder.find('.ipsDataList > li:visible').removeClass('even').filter(function(index, element){
                         return index % 2;
                     }).addClass('even')
                 }
             });
         };
 
 
         var checkForumCookies = function () {
             var cookie = getCookie('hiddenIds');
             cookie = decodeURIComponent(cookie);
             if (cookie != null) {
                 var temp = cookie.split(';');
                 if ((temp != null) && (temp.length > 0)) {
                     for (var i = 0; i < temp.length; i++) {
                         var values = temp[i].split('_');
                         var catId = String(values[0]);
                         var forumId = String(values[1]);
                         if (catId != '') {
                             if (hiddenIds[catId] == null) {
                                 hiddenIds[catId] = [];
                             }
                             hiddenIds[catId].push(forumId);
                         }
                     }
                 }
             }
             renderHiddenForums();
         };
 
         $(document).ready(function () {
             addForumCloseLinks();
             checkForumCookies();
         });
 
     }(jQuery));
       </script>

             <br/>
             Tipp dir den Kick
            </li>

             </a>

             </a>
             <br/>
             Sportwetten mit Erfolg
            </li>
           </ul>
          </div>
